text: Al-Khutoot Al-Jawiya Sport Club (), is an Iraqi football team based in Al-A'amiriya, Baghdad, that plays in the Iraq Division One and Iraq FA Cup. ==Honours== ===Domestic=== ====National==== *Iraq FA Cup **Runners-up (1): 1991–92 ==See also== * 2012–13 Iraq FA Cup * 2015–16 Iraq FA Cup * 2016–17 Iraq FA Cup * 2018–19 Iraq FA Cup ==References== ==External links== * Al- Khutoot profile at kooora.com (in Arabic) * Iraq Clubs- Foundation Dates Category:Football clubs in Iraq Category:Sport in Baghdad
